'''聯合國原子能委員會'''('''UNAEC''')是[[聯合國|聯合國]][[安全理事會|安全理事會]]直屬的機構之一，1946年1月24日成立於[[倫敦|倫敦]]，其任務為研究、調查、管制有關[[原子能|原子能]]的一般事項。<ref name="UN_ARES1I">{{UN document |docid=A-RES-1(I) |type=Resolution |body=General Assembly |session=1 |resolution_number=1 |accessdate=2010-06-18|date=24 January 1946|title=Establishment of a Commission to Deal with the Problems Raised by the Discovery of Atomic Energy}}</ref>

联合国大会正式解散UNAEC于1952年，虽然委员会自1949年7月一直处于非活动状态。<ref>[[International_Atomic_Energy_Agency|International Atomic Energy Agency]], "IAEA Turns 40: Key Dates & Historical Developments," Supplement to the IAEA Bulletin, September 1997, {{cite web |url=http://www.iaea.org/Publications/Magazines/Bulletin/Bull393/Chronology/chronology.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-06-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611111203/http://iaea.org/Publications/Magazines/Bulletin/Bull393/Chronology/chronology.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-11 }}</ref>

